<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us | Community Help Exchange</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f3f8fc;
            color: #1f2937;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #38bdf8);
            color: white;
            padding: 56px 20px;
        }

        .hero-inner {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .mini-title {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .nav-row {
            margin-top: 22px;
        }

        .nav-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            background: white;
            color: #1d4ed8;
            border-radius: 999px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .page {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 24px 16px 40px;
        }

        .section-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        .section-card h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #1d4ed8;
        }

        .section-card p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
            gap: 18px;
            align-items: stretch;
        }

        .photo-box {
            background: #e0f2fe;
            border: 2px dashed #38bdf8;
            border-radius: 16px;
            min-height: 260px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 18px;
            color: #0369a1;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .team-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .member-card {
            background: #eef4ff;
            padding: 18px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            border-top: 5px solid #2563eb;
        }

        .member-card h3 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            color: #1f2937;
        }

        .member-card p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background: #eef2ff;
            border-left: 5px solid #4f46e5;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-top: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .about-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-inner">
            <p class="mini-title">Meet the Team</p>
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">
                Learn more about our team, our project, and why we created Community Help Exchange.
            </p>

            <div class="nav-row">
                <a href="/" class="nav-btn">Back to Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="page">
        <section class="section-card">
            <div class="about-grid">
                <div>
                    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                    <p>
                        We are a hackathon team focused on building a simple and useful tool
                        that helps people find community resources more easily. Our goal was
                        to create a website that feels welcoming, easy to use, and helpful
                        for people looking for food support, shelter help, campus resources,
                        and donation centers.
                    </p>

                    <div class="highlight-box">
                        Our mission is to make support easier to find by organizing local
                        resources in one simple place.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="photo-box">
                    Add your team photo here
                    <br><br>
                    Replace this box with a real image later
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section-card">
            <h2>Our Team</h2>
            <div class="team-grid">
                <div class="member-card">
                    <h3>Your Name</h3>
                    <p>Describe your role here. For example: design, coding, research, or presentation.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="member-card">
                    <h3>Teammate Name</h3>
                    <p>Describe what this teammate contributed to the web app and project idea.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="member-card">
                    <h3>Teammate Name</h3>
                    <p>Describe their role and what they helped create for the website.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="member-card">
                    <h3>Teammate Name</h3>
                    <p>Add another teammate here if needed, along with their contribution.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section-card">
            <h2>Why We Created This Website</h2>
            <p>
                We created Community Help Exchange because finding help should not feel confusing
                or overwhelming. We wanted to make a website that is simple, clear, and practical
                so users can quickly find resources without wasting time.
            </p>
            <p>
                This project represents our effort to support the community through technology
                by making important information easier to access.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>